Game::EnergyLoop - a simple energy system

This module can be installed using cpanm.

    cpanm Game::EnergyLoop

Run perldoc(1) on Game::EnergyLoop for documentation.


To author a new release,

    perl Build.PL
    RELEASE_TESTING=1 ./Build test
    ./Build testcover
    ./Build disttest
    git tag -u ... -s v...
    ./Build dist
    cpan-upload ...
    git push ...
    ./Build realclean
